RecallContext is a Form
    Layout
        four column distributed
            paragraph
                visible when (not RecallNoticeExists)
                    RecallGroup
                visible when (RecallNoticeExists)
                    RecallGroup
                        display as text
                RecallGroup.Description
                    no label
                    display as text
            RecallNotice
                display as text
            WorkingId
                display as text
            Status
                display as text
        five column distributed
            Name
            visible when (QueryHasBeenRun)
                LastProductActivityQuery
                    label is "LastQueryRunDate"
                    display as text
            visible when (ProductsUpdatedAfterQueryRunDate)
                text of "*ProductsHaveBeenUpdatedSinceLastQueryRun"
                    italics
            visible when (ItemProposal)
                ProposedItem
                    label is "NewItemProposalStatus"
                    display as text
            visible when (TrialEndDateEntered)
                TrialEndDate
                    display as text
